    <h2> Mathematical Software Cross Index</h2> 
    <p>Search for software according to</p>
    <ul>
      <li> Browse the <a href="cgi-bin/serve.cgi">Problem Taxonomy.</a></li>
      <li> Search the Taxonomy by <a href="Problem.html">problem keywords</a>. </li>
      <li> Browse the <a href="cgi-bin/serve.cgi/Packages">Package List</a>. </li>
      <li> Search for modules by <a href="Search.html">name or keyword</a>. </li>
    </ul>
 
    <!--
    <p><b>Try <a href="HotGAMS/">HotGAMS</a>, a Java interface to GAMS with additional
